{"type": "article", "id": 20979, "title": "智能吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-20T07:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125720rjNX6BofcbITDl5t.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款可以控制光源方向的灯，它当然也可以调整强弱更换颜色。它的外形非常普通，内含 300 个 LED 灯，可以通过智能手机上的程序控制，当光源转动时，似乎有了聚光灯的效果。此外，它还安装感应系统，可以判断房间里是否有人来打开或关闭灯。定价 449 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/fluxo-the-world-s-first-truly-smart-lamp--2#/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261507068A2iI7QmLdHnKTXW.gif\" width=\"516\" height=\"344\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150707AUkdylOwIV8g2xTS.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"418\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67419355\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150707yUD8euFmbB1iv7Wf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"726\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150708F7SaIk8optV2TciC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"727\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150708BvzdLaksZ7gQqNT1.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"561\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.90483871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}